# Installation
- install uv 

# Run
- Set database username and password in settings.py file
- go to project dir
- run -> uv run main.py

# Claude setup
Before running query in claude, follow these steps:
- Add resource file in claude chat
- Add prompt in claude chat
- Enter your query

# File details
- tools.py -> MCP tools
- resources.py -> MCP resources
- prompt.py -> MCP prompt
- settings.py -> settings file
- main.py -> MCP main
- server.py -> sets global mcp object
- helper.py -> helper functions

- sql_permitted_tables.json -> resource file for permitted tables
